  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, your snacks speed enhancing effects extend to their aroma, granting you an additional Aura.</p><p> You may activate this Aura once, then twice at 14th level, per Long Rest without spending a use of your Auras.</p><p> Expediting Scent: Allied creatures who enter, or start their turns within, this Aura gain the benefits of the disengage action, and have advantage on saving throws as a result of entering or starting their turns within an area, until the end of their turn.</p><p> Additionally, when you eat a Snack as a part of rolling Initiative, you may activate this Aura as a reaction, giving each creature, of your choice, within the Aura advantage on their Initiative check.</p><p></p>",
